	* Eliminated warnings

2001-06-11 14:43  tshead

	* aqsis/: .cvsignore, aqsis.cpp: * Added "--help" and "--version"
	command-line options.  * By default, a standard set of arguments is
	declared before processing any RIB files.  This behaviour can be
	turned off with the "--nostandard" option.  * If no RIB files are
	specified on the command-line, automatically parses RIB from stdin.

